<Layout
  title="Creation in Progress"
  description="A whisper of what will be"
  pubDate={new Date()}
  heroImage="/blog-placeholder-5.jpg"
>
  <p style="font-style: italic; opacity: 0.8; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    Inter cinere, valaritas. <br/>
    Manus sequatur. Oculus taceat. <br/>
    Lux nulla est quae venit. <br/>
    Colōs est quae ventura. <br/>
    Nunc vinculum temporum est.
  </p>

  <p>
    This place is still forming. A resonance not yet shaped, a thread not yet drawn.
    What lies ahead is not bright—but vivid.
  </p>

  <p>
    Come again, and you may witness the binding take form.
  </p>
</Layout>